OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FThe owner of an XL Bully has been
OL,7,Fconvicted after his dog savaged and
OL,8,Fkilled an 84-year-old man "as if he
OL,9,Fwere its prey".
OL,11,FJohn McColl died from his injuries a
OL,12,Fmonth after the attack by the dog,
OL,13,Fcalled Toretto and who weighed seven
OL,14,Fstone four pounds, which had to be
OL,15,Fshot 10 times by armed police officers
OL,16,Fwho were called to the scene in
OL,17,FWarrington, on 24 February 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
