FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FSean Garner, 31, previously admitted
OL,7,Fpossessing the banned male dog and a
OL,8,Ffemale of the same breed without an
OL,9,Fexemption certificate but denied being
OL,10,Fthe owner of a dog which caused injury
OL,11,Fwhile dangerously out of control.
OL,13,FBut following a week-long trial at
OL,14,FLiverpool Crown Court, Garner was
OL,15,Ffound unanimously guilty.
OL,17,FHe showed no reaction as the verdict
OL,18,Fwas returned, but members of his
OL,19,Ffamily were in tears in the public
OL,20,Fgallery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FA trial heard the attack happened
OL,7,Fafter Mr McColl wandered onto the
OL,8,Fdriveway of Garner's property in
OL,9,FBardsley Avenue, at about 6pm.
OL,11,FThe dog had been left on a patio area
OL,12,Fwhich the prosecution alleged was only
OL,13,Fsecured by a gate with a latch.
OL,15,FA member of the public heard Mr McColl
OL,16,Fscreaming for help, and neighbours
OL,17,Fdescribed using items including a
OL,18,Fspirit level and a walking stick to
OL,19,Ftry and get the dog away from Mr
OL,20,FMcColl, a widowed dad-of-three and
OL,21,Fgrandfather.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FDavid Birrell, prosecuting, said:
OL,7,F"After he entered the defendant's
OL,8,Fdriveway, that dog, that XL bully,
OL,9,Fattacked him and it just would not let
OL,10,Fhim go.
OL,12,F"People tried to help him. Grown men,
OL,13,Fwith weapons, hitting the dog. But it
OL,14,Fwas no use.
OL,16,F"The dog guarded him as if he were its
OL,17,Fprey. It savaged him."
OL,19,FAn examination of the dog later found
OL,20,Fit had no food in its stomach, but it
OL,21,Fhad begun to eat Mr McColl alive.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FGiving evidence, Garner, who has
OL,7,Fprevious convictions for driving
OL,8,Foffences and possessing drugs with
OL,9,Fintent to supply, claimed he took
OL,10,Fsteps to ensure Toretto and the second
OL,11,FXL bully, a female called Malibu who
OL,12,Fwas shot when police found her inside
OL,13,Fthe house, were not dangerously out of
OL,14,Fcontrol.
OL,16,FHe claimed the dog was locked inside a
OL,17,Fshed on the patio outside his home and
OL,18,Fdisagreed that the dog was hungry,
OL,19,Fdespite an examination finding there
OL,20,Fwas no dog food in its stomach.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FPolice officers called to the scene
OL,7,Fcould not get to Mr McColl so firearms
OL,8,Fofficers attended and shot the dog
OL,9,Fnine times with a pistol and once with
OL,10,Fa shotgun, the court heard.
OL,12,FA second dog, called Malibu, was also
OL,13,Fshot by police who "didn't take any
OL,14,Fchances", Mr Birrell said.
OL,16,FGarner told the court at the time of
OL,17,Fthe attack he did not know the dogs'
OL,18,Fbreed, which was banned in 2024,
OL,19,Falthough the court heard he had
OL,20,Fpreviously advertised Malibu for
OL,21,Fbreeding as an XL bully on Instagram.
OL,26,@uD@TOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FHe said he had not walked the dogs for
OL,7,Fabout 10 days, but said he had allowed
OL,8,Fthem onto the patio for exercise.
OL,10,FGarner, who described Toretto as
OL,11,F"missing a few nuts and bolts" in a
OL,12,Fmessage to his mother, told the court:
OL,13,F"I could never imagine that a man who
OL,14,Fhas been the pub could go up my path
OL,15,Fon his way home and do what he has
OL,16,Fobviously done to let my dog out."
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@^O]uD@AOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FThe jury was told Garner avoided
OL,7,Fpolice for two days before handing
OL,8,Fhimself in on February 26. He said he
OL,9,Fdid not return to his home when police
OL,10,Frang him about the incident because he
OL,11,Fwas disqualified from driving and did
OL,12,Fnot want officers to see him in a
OL,13,Fvehicle.
OL,15,FGarner agreed he was a "coward" to
OL,16,Finstead allow his pregnant partner to
OL,17,Freturn to the house with their two
OL,18,Fchildren, which led to police
OL,19,Farresting her.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FIn his closing speech, Mr Birrell
OL,7,Fdescribed Garner as a "selfish,
OL,8,Freckless risk taker who couldn't care
OL,9,Fless" and told "bare-faced lies".
OL,11,FHe said Garner's claims that Mr McColl
OL,12,Fhad released the "big, savage dog"
OL,13,Ffrom a padlocked shed were "ludicrous"
OL,14,Fand "absurd".
OL,26,@oD@WOUqD@EO]qD@POUqD@`O]tD@ROUtD@bO]uD@
OL,26,A\OUuD@fO]vD@EOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FSpeaking outside Liverpool Crown
OL,7,FCourt, Detective Sergeant Emily Cole
OL,8,Fsaid: "Today's circumstances of the
OL,9,Fcase, highlight the very reason the
OL,10,Fdangerous dog act exists and the
OL,11,Fdangerous consequences that can occur
OL,12,Fwhen the law is not followed.
OL,14,F"Mr McColl was an 84-year-old dad,
OL,15,Fgrandad and great-grandad. On the
OL,16,Fnight of the incident he was simply
OL,17,Fwalking home and contrary to previous
OL,18,Frumours he wasn't drunk but he became
OL,19,Fdistracted and entered the driveway of
OL,20,Fa property that was being rented by Mr
OL,21,FGarner.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,F"We may never know precisely why he
OL,7,Fentered the driveway, but what is
OL,8,Fclear is that the dog was not securely
OL,9,Fcontained. As a result, Toretto
OL,10,Fattacked and killed Mr McColl.
OL,12,F"This incident could have happened to
OL,13,Fanyone who might have that driveway
OL,14,Fthat day, whether that was a postman,
OL,15,Fdelivery driver or a child collecting
OL,16,Fa ball.
OL,18,F"Sadly, it was Mr McColl who was that
OL,19,Fperson."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,FMs Cole added: "Sean Garner knew that
OL,7,FToretto was an unregistered XL Bully.
OL,8,FHe was well aware of the dog's
OL,9,Fdestructive and aggressive tendencies.
OL,11,F"Yet despite this, he chose to leave
OL,12,Fthe dog outside his address in an
OL,13,Finsecure area. Not only that, but he
OL,14,Fkept a second unregistered XL Bully
OL,15,Fwithin the same property.
OL,17,F"His actions that day resulted in the
OL,18,Fdeath of an innocent man.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774987556
OL,3,COwner of XL Bully guilty over attack
OL,4,Cwhich 'savaged' and killed elderly man
OL,6,F"Our thoughts and deepest sympathies
OL,7,Fare with the family of Mr. McColl.
OL,8,FWhat they witnessed as he suffered
OL,9,Funimaginable injuries is beyond
OL,10,Fcomprehension. The strength and
OL,11,Fdetermination Mr. McColl showed in
OL,12,Ffighting to survive those injuries was
OL,13,Fboth astonishing and deeply inspiring."
OL,15,FGarner, now of Belle Vale, Liverpool,
OL,16,Fpreviously admitted two counts of
OL,17,Fpossessing an XL bully without an
OL,18,Fexemption certificate.
OL,20,FHe is due to be sentenced on April 17.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
